signatures.text: inline fun <T> toComponents( action: (days: Long, hours: Int, minutes: Int, seconds: Int, nanoseconds: Int) -> T): T
signatures.desc: Splits this duration into days, hours, minutes, seconds, and nanoseconds and executes the given action with these components. The result of action is returned as the result of this function.
